{"tid":736497,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想搞一個全港都可以參加，亦都需要嘅活動","createTime":"2018-07-10T09:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T14:18:33.000Z","uid":190472,"like":27,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"581c7155688f0ad5376526b5ac11afb6ae9aee1f","tid":736497,"uid":190472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"好少話有D咩活動可以全港市民一齊參與<br />\n正值DSE考生等放榜，壓力一定大，始終成世食粥食飯就睇今鋪<br />\n更唔講上班一族日日OT，積積埋埋唔少怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想臨時舉辦一個活動，大家都可以參與 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係起某個時間，一齊向天咆哮 (真係大叫)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個咆哮有個靚名，就叫「佛洛哥斯塔咆哮」(Flogsta Scream)<br />\n大家唔洗怕羞，起屋企鳩叫無人知你係邊個<br />\n唔想打搞屋企人，可以行多兩步出門鳩叫<br />\n約埋朋友一齊叫又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想起香港搞返次一樣嘅，我覺得真係一個唔錯嘅習俗黎<br />\n約定你地今晚10點正 (7月10日)<br />\n咩地方都得，一齊向天咆哮<br />\n活動持續5分鐘左右，廢事過份滋擾到附近居民<br />\n因為真係好Q嘈，所以請大家節制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n據說是起源於1970年代<br />\n當時有位學生因考試壓力太大，因而選擇結束自己的生命<br />\n而後學生們開始透過對窗外大聲吼叫的方式，來紓解課業的壓力<br />\n久而久之就變成了一種傳統<br />\n<br />\n簡單介紹咩係「佛洛哥斯塔咆哮」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=spjMWVbtl78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DspjMWVbtl78&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=2e1e82db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=spjMWVbtl78</a><br />\n<br />\n活動專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1759758084131089/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1759758084131089%2F&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=b38b13ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1759758084131089/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得OK嘅 真心歡迎你分享出去(因為好快夠鐘)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都可以考慮下將佢成為一個習俗<br />\n逢星期三10點可以鳩叫5分鐘之類<br />\n<br />\n不過講到尾，無論學生定成年人都好<br />\n請珍惜自己嘅生命，因為世界真係好大好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33285db53845663000fd7dc186c0f2ba14ba8365","tid":736497,"uid":118463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e907244fb82af087535bcb2de7a439271ca78c","tid":736497,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8e7c6fd614b45258c76984472b1ca7e798ce205d","tid":736497,"uid":4724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"見到標題我只會諗起普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7049cc84f5dfe49d998276a2a8653ba052bbc4bf","tid":736497,"uid":190472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7c6fd614b45258c76984472b1ca7e798ce205d","tid":736497,"uid":4724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"見到標題我只會諗起普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"我邊有咁大後台可以搞普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54c511d058ceba4c589e65cfa7a0a45167fb917","tid":736497,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"個個掛住搵錢 去玩 邊個風閒理"},{"pid":"691c1202dc60ae98696a5f2375c880fdf402865c","tid":736497,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"睇錯左嗌「佛洛哥斯塔咆哮」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62e873301632ebda35d1fd80ee2221a054c1b2c","tid":736497,"uid":190472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f54c511d058ceba4c589e65cfa7a0a45167fb917","tid":736497,"uid":138197,"like":0,"di